c: 2
v: 153
t: "ya 'ayuha almuminun atlbu aleawn min allah fi kl amwrkm: bialsabr ealaa alnwayb walmsayb, wtrk almeasy waldhnwb, walsbr ealaa altaeat walqrbat, walsalat alty tatmayinu biha alnfs, wtnha ean alfahsha' walmnkr. 'iina allah mae alsaabirin bieawnih wtwfyqh wtsdydh. wafi alayt: 'iithbat meyat allah alkhasat balmwmnyn, almqtdyt lamaa salaf dhkrh; 'amaa almeyt aleamt, almqtdyt llelm wal'ihatt fahi lajamie alkhlq"